Devoted Spirit (Counter)
Level: Crusader 2, Saint 2
Initiation Action: 1 immediate action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Instantaneous

As an immediate action, you can grant an AC bonus to an adjacent ally equal to your shield's AC bonus + 4. You apply this bonus in response to a single melee or ranged attack that targets your ally.  You must have a shield equipped in order to initiate this maneuver.
